{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"General Rule","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Section 453A(d) of the 1986 Code (relating to pledges, etc., of installment obligations) shall not apply to any pledge after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-12-17"},"text":"December 17, 1987","children":[],"tail":", of an installment obligation to secure any indebtedness if such indebtedness is incurred to refinance indebtedness which was outstanding on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-12-17"},"text":"December 17, 1987","children":[],"tail":", and which was secured on such date and all times thereafter before such refinancing by a pledge of such installment obligation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"“(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Limitation","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Subsection (a) shall not apply to the extent that the principal amount of the indebtedness resulting from the refinancing exceeds the principal amount of the refinanced indebtedness immediately before the refinancing.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"“(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Certain Refinancings Permitted","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of subsection (a), if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"“(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a refinancing is attributable to the calling of indebtedness by the creditor, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"“(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" such refinancing is not with the creditor under the refinanced indebtedness or a person related to such creditor,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"such refinancing shall, to the extent the refinanced indebtedness qualifies under subsections (a) and (b), be treated as a continuation of such refinanced indebtedness.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id4381bd4d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514","children":[],"tail":" Treated as Change in Method of Accounting"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For provisions requiring change in accounting method in the case of any taxpayer who made sales under revolving credit plan and was on installment method under this section for such taxpayer’s last taxable year beginning before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1987","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/s812/c/2"},"text":"section 812(c)(2) of Pub. L. 99–514","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date of 1986 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s453"},"text":"section 453 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
